1.title: Introduction - Part 1

episode of.title: Warp Drive Physics: Prepare for Warp Speed (TV Series 2018– )

1.plot: A warp drive is a theoretical faster-than-light spacecraft propulsion system. A spacecraft equipped with a warp drive may travel at speeds greater than that of light by many orders of magnitude. In this course we realistically entertain the notion of a warp drive and explore the current scientific advances in the field.
